data.name: SourceVB
data.value: Public Function Convert(value As Object, targetType As Type, parameter As Object, culture As CultureInfo) As Object If TypeOf parameter Is String Then Dim dict = TryCast(value, Dictionary(Of String, Object)) If dict IsNot Nothing Then Dim parameters As String() = DirectCast(parameter, String).Split(":"C) Dim key As String = parameters(0) If parameters.Length >= 2 Then Dim format As String = parameters(1) Return [String].Format("{0:" & format & "}", dict(key)) End If Return dict(key) End If End If Return String.Empty End Function
